1 AN ACT concerning alcoholic beverages; relating to eligibility for
2 licensure under the Kansas liquor control act and the club and drinking
3 establishment act; authorizing the director of alcoholic beverage control
4 to issue licenses to convicted felons when such conviction occurred
5 more than 10 years prior to application for a license and a
6 determination of sufficient rehabilitation is made; amending K.S.A. 41-
7 2623 and K.S.A. 2024 Supp. 41-311 and repealing the existing
8 sections.
